358
00:30:07,262 --> 00:30:10,232
Salimos a truco o trato, volvimos a casa...

359
00:30:10,265 --> 00:30:12,840
...y fuiste a enchufar unas luces y...

360
00:30:14,269 --> 00:30:16,800
- Mi mujer.
